   "source": [
    "* Normally, you would know the IP of the machine you deploy your app to or there would be a DNS registration to let you use a URL.\n",
    "    * For our purposes today, we need to find that out and also to find out each one of our unique port numbers.\n",
    "* The following Python functions will do that for us."
   ]
